	#. Write the following sets in set builder notation.

	> a) The plane with normal vector $\left< 1, 3, 4 \right>$.

	> b) The set of points in $#R#^3$ with positive $x$-, $y$-, and $z$-coordinates.

	> c) The set of points in $#R#^4$ with distance $1$ from the origin. What do you think this set looks like?

